    "created_at": "2015-07-09T03:49:48Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-09T03:49:48Z",
    "body": "You have to set `returnValue` when handling synchronous messages:\nhttps://github.com/atom/electron/blob/master/docs/api/ipc-main-process.md\n\nOtherwise the web page would wait for responses forever.\n"
  },
