    "created_at": "2015-07-09T15:40:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-09T15:47:00Z",
    "body": "Understood. The documentation should be updated with a note that setting `event.returnValue` is a required step for `sendSync`. Its not intuitive to set `event.returnValue=null`.\n"
  },
