    "created_at": "2015-07-09T15:44:33Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-09T15:46:32Z",
    "body": "Is it possible to update the logic behind `ipc.sendSync()` to have the setting of `returnValue` optional? I am sure that others will get burned by the same issue and silent fails are very nasty to hit for developers.\n"
  },
